aces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但唔比扑"},{"pid":"e146426638f3505c7cd1b1e968d96d3ab275a824","tid":258301,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T04:20:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我滿心歡喜以為復合成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知佢冷淡過以前好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nwts成日已讀不回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想撩佢曳曳佢又唔so我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試過復合成功,條女性格變曬.<br />\n之前係佢追我...&hellip;之後係我復合.<br />\n總之復合慘過地底泥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好中！！！莊閒逆轉左，宜家比佢食住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8475678a82dec66d951b7c814cf9c5f91cb84420","tid":258301,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T04:21:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>上次點解散 今次邊個追返邊個 一齊返幾耐</blockquote><br />\n佢話感情淡左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我煩左佢2個月先復合有拖手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但唔比扑</blockquote><br />\n姐係返撻唔比扑？<br />\n如果係咁佢唔多so妳 姐係當妳係雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"213c3039940e552fc869acd57997c170cddf3429","tid":258301,"uid":47281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T04:25:30.000Z","msg":"逝去感情如何留得住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n身邊朋友有散左復合都好sweet<br />\n但我覺得大前題係雙方都好愛對方有意復合<br />\n而唔係單方面又唉又西乞番黎<br />\n<br />\n我自己就<br />\n諗得清清楚楚先講分手 一分就死都唔會番轉頭<br />\n利申 無後悔<br />\n<br />\n樓豬自己諗清楚 support<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b1712d8a3555974f1c66eabeccb3139b19fc1e9","tid":258301,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20